    <section id="tribute-info">
      <h2 id="accomplishments">Timeline of NIGO's career</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>1970-</strong> born Tomoaki Nagao in Maebashi, Japan </li>
        <li><strong>1993-</strong> opened a retail clothing store, NOWHERE</li>
        <li><strong>1994-</strong> started his brand BAPE</li>
        <li><strong>2003-</strong> released BAPESTA model shoe</li>
        <li><strong>2010-</strong> started new company Human Made</li>
        <li><strong>2011-</strong> sold 90% of BAPE to Honk Kong company I.T.</li>
        <li><strong>2021-</strong> appointed as creative director of Kenzo</li>
      </ul>
      
      
    </section>
   
